## Third-Party Services

This add-on uses the following external APIs:

1. **Romaji2Kana API** (https://api.romaji2kana.com)
   - Used for Japanese character reading conversions
   - Subject to their terms of service and rate limits

2. **KanjiAPI** (https://kanjiapi.dev)
   - Used for kanji information and meanings
   - Subject to their terms of service and rate limits

Users are responsible for complying with the terms of service of these external APIs.

## Disclaimer

This add-on is provided as-is without any warranty. The accuracy of the generated
glossaries depends on the external APIs used. The author is not responsible for
any inaccuracies in the generated content or any issues arising from the use
of external services.
